92
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:31,420
But when again they had preached,

93
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:32,100
we say to ourselves,

94
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:33,160
What did they preach?

95
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:35,580
Do you realize Jesus never wrote a word,

96
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:36,560
