97
00:06:36,820 --> 00:06:39,840
We have no record of any writing of Jesus.

98
00:06:40,340 --> 00:06:41,980
It was written for him.

99
00:06:42,380 --> 00:06:45,740
The Holy Spirit therefore wrote down what Jesus had taught

100
00:06:45,740 --> 00:06:47,440
and what the disciples had preached,

101
00:06:47,780 --> 00:06:49,840
that you and I might know the truth.

102
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:50,800
Jesus said,

103
00:06:50,900 --> 00:06:52,520
If you continue in my word,

104
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:53,840
you shall know the truth,

105
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:55,260
and the truth shall make you free.

106
00:06:55,260 --> 00:06:58,920
