00:07:58,300 --> 00:08:00,200
that the Apostle Peter has left us.

144
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,800
The three letters of John

145
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:02,920
besides the Gospel.

146
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:04,000
And then finally,

147
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:04,700
the revelation,

148
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:05,460
the Apocalypse.

149
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,660
God has given us this record

150
00:08:07,660 --> 00:08:09,160
by inspiration.

151
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:10,960
And it was Martin Luther

152
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:12,460
